### Linting

- Config is in [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js) and targets `**/*.{ts,tsx}`.
- Extends `@eslint/js` and `typescript-eslint` recommended configs.
- Enforces React Hooks rules via `eslint-plugin-react-hooks`.
- Warns if files export non-components with React Fast Refresh enabled: `react-refresh/only-export-components`.
- Browser globals are enabled via `globals.browser`.

